BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 607.00 Tm (Land the superpower in the key box: because the two sides only agree on the data format and the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 592.60 Tm (URLs, neither cares what language the other is written in. A Python app, a React front-end, and an) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 578.20 Tm (Android phone can all call the same Java API. That independence is called loose coupling, and it's why) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 563.80 Tm (web services scale across teams and technologies.) Tj ET
