BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 394.00 Tm (at-PutMapping, and at-DeleteMapping map the four verbs. At-PathVariable pulls a value from the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 379.00 Tm (URL path; at-RequestParam pulls a query parameter; at-RequestBody turns the incoming JSON) Tj ET
